# HR Analytics Dashboard (Excel)

## Objective
To analyze HR data and build an interactive dashboard to track workforce metrics and support HR decision-making.

## Dataset
- Employee dataset containing department, age, attrition, and headcount information

## Key Metrics Analyzed
- Total headcount
- Attrition rate
- Department-wise employee distribution
- Average employee age

## Dashboard Features
- Interactive Pivot Tables
- Charts and slicers for department-level insights
- Visual representation of attrition trends

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
